Css can be of three types
i. External 
ii. Internal 
iii. Inline

For course point of view wer will be using internal css and for industry point of view external css is preffered.

Eg.
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <head>
        <title>CSS </title>
        <!--<link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
        -->
        <style>
            body{
            background-color: greenyellow;
            }
            h1 {
            color: blue
            }
            p{
            color: red
            }
        </style>
    </head>
    <body>
        <h1> H1 Heading</h1>
        <p> P Paragraph</p>
    </body>
</html>
